WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.267
Well, good evening family.

00:00:01.267 --> 00:00:02.240
Praise the Lord.

00:00:02.240 --> 00:00:05.720
Thank you for joining us again tonight on this Sunday.

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:08.067
What a wonderful day it's been.

00:00:11.635 --> 00:00:12.810
You know, the weather's been really pretty in the state of Oklahoma.

00:00:12.810 --> 00:00:15.055
We're believing for more rain.

00:00:15.055 --> 00:00:18.760
We need a lot more rain.

00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:25.080
I don't know where you are, but I bet you need rain, too.

00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:31.960
And so, we're going to continue to pray for the rain over this nation.

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:37.505
I know there's a lot of people that are in drought.

00:00:41.524 --> 00:00:46.377
And so, before we get into the summer, we only have just a couple more weeks and we'll be into the hot months.

00:00:50.253 --> 00:00:52.065
So, we really need to fill up our lakes and our streams.

00:00:55.020 --> 00:00:55.250
And Colorado needs rain desperately.

00:00:59.470 --> 00:01:06.400
And so, we're going to call it in.

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:07.451
We're going to believe God.

00:01:07.451 --> 00:01:08.857
And that's what we always do.

00:01:08.857 --> 00:01:11.440
We're going to believe God and we're going to get some rain.

00:01:11.742 --> 00:01:22.143
You know, I just thought about all the things that the Lord has done this week and just being thankful for every single thing that he has done, giving him holy praise.

00:01:22.143 --> 00:01:29.880
Like Paul and Silas in the midnight hour giving him praise in the prison and the walls began to shake.

00:01:29.880 --> 00:01:34.120
They weren't praying, they were praising.

00:01:34.120 --> 00:01:39.275
And in the praise, God delivered them out of the prison.

00:01:39.275 --> 00:01:43.171
And I think tonight's a good night for whatever you've been through this week.

00:01:43.171 --> 00:01:46.340
The walls will begin to shake in your life.

00:01:46.340 --> 00:01:49.765
The walls that have held you back, that have held you captive.

00:01:49.765 --> 00:02:05.760
I feel it in my heart tonight that the Lord is saying, if you just give me some praise where you are, in your circumstance, the walls that have been holding you captive will begin to shake in your life.

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:08.775
And I know that this is true.

00:02:08.775 --> 00:02:11.645
I felt it in my spirit as I was praying this afternoon.

00:02:11.645 --> 00:02:18.107
And he said, I've done some good things, Brandon, and a lot of people, I've healed their bodies.

00:02:18.107 --> 00:02:20.791
I've delivered them from some things.

00:02:20.791 --> 00:02:24.448
And I need some gratitude.

00:02:24.448 --> 00:02:25.024
Some gratitude.

00:02:27.914 --> 00:02:33.680
Let's just praise him for just a couple minutes for everything he's done in your life.

00:02:33.680 --> 00:02:37.528
You may say, Well, Brandon, I just have just a little bit of a breakthrough.

00:02:37.528 --> 00:02:42.080
Praise him for the breakthrough that you have.

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:47.640
Praise him for where you are, that you're not where you used to be.

00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:52.400
And I believe in doing so the manifestation of what you're believing for.

00:02:52.400 --> 00:02:54.080
There's an expiration date on it.

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:59.816
And I'm telling you, I believe with all my heart that God is a God that will deliver his people.

00:02:59.816 --> 00:03:04.239
And there's expiration dates to what you've been believing for.

00:03:04.589 --> 00:03:07.394
All things are possible to him who believes.

00:03:07.394 --> 00:03:12.840
So, Father, we just give you praise and glory and honor for this prayer time tonight.

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:17.056
We praise you, Father, for the breakthrough, for whatever they're believing for.

00:03:17.056 --> 00:03:27.519
Father, in their health, in their minds and their emotions and their marriages, Father, we thank you, Lord, for the week that we had, and I thank you for the week that we're about to start.

00:03:27.519 --> 00:03:34.109
We're so grateful, Father, that you have showed up and showed off in our lives over the month of April.

00:03:34.474 --> 00:03:40.400
There were so many breakthroughs and so many things that we saw in prayer.

00:03:40.400 --> 00:03:43.430
And Lord, we thank you for the month of May.

00:03:43.430 --> 00:03:51.674
We start out this month of May, Father, with great expectation for great turnaround in our circumstances.

00:03:51.674 --> 00:03:59.044
No matter what it is that we're believing for, Father, we're believing for exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:03:59.044 --> 00:04:01.720
So, Father, we dedicate this month to you.

00:04:01.720 --> 00:04:14.120
We dedicate the month of May that this will be the beginning of supernatural blessing and increase, healing, marriages restored, children coming home, whatever they may need.

00:04:14.120 --> 00:04:18.548
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we praise you in that midnight hour.

00:04:18.548 --> 00:04:23.503
And I believe the walls of our circumstances are shaking right now.

00:04:23.503 --> 00:04:24.166
They're shaking.

00:04:24.166 --> 00:04:28.480
And I thank you, Lord, that Father, the chains have been broken.

00:04:28.480 --> 00:04:43.780
You were crucified for us and Father you were resurrected on the third day and you dwell in us in the name of Jesus richly by faith and we believe that Father the breakthrough of what we're believing for is right at hand.

00:04:43.780 --> 00:04:57.680
Jobs and better jobs, raises and bonuses, benefits, sales and commissions, growth in businesses and states and inheritances, rebates and returns, checks in the mail, gifts and surprises.

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:59.033
Do you believe that?

00:04:59.033 --> 00:05:06.360
Finding money, bills paid off, blessing and increase, healing in your body, from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

00:05:06.360 --> 00:05:10.480
I believe that God is a rewarder of those that diligently seek him.

00:05:10.480 --> 00:05:13.989
And Father, we thank you, Lord, that you're the healer and you're the deliverer.

00:05:13.989 --> 00:05:22.960
And Father, we thank you for the good things that we're about to see in the rest of this year, 2026.

00:05:31.024 --> 00:05:31.528
We are ahead of schedule.

00:05:32.032 --> 00:05:32.536
2026.

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:33.536
Wow.

00:05:33.536 --> 00:05:35.520
Where have I been?

00:05:37.160 --> 00:05:41.550
Interesting.

00:05:41.560 --> 00:05:44.200
When I was seeing it over in the spirit realm.

00:05:46.200 --> 00:05:57.030
There was things I was seeing over just not even an hour ago.

00:05:57.040 --> 00:06:01.560
And it was concerning the years and what the Lord is showing me.

00:06:04.400 --> 00:06:09.790
2026, 2027.

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:13.560
Where are we at in 2027?

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:15.135
What does 2027 look like?

00:06:15.135 --> 00:06:19.080
But what does the rest of 2026 look like?

00:06:19.080 --> 00:06:29.680
And as I was looking over into it, as I was praying, he said, I have some things I need to show you before you start your live stream.

00:06:29.680 --> 00:06:40.870
And the shaking of our nation, the shaking of the nations.

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:46.320
We've never been in a time like we're about to see.

00:06:46.320 --> 00:07:07.360
When the Lord said in 2025, that's what he said on September the 23rd, you would enter into the point of no return, the point of acceleration whenever they had the UN meeting and it was all about Israel and the things that were taking place and then we entered into this year.

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:09.530
But I'm trying to warn you.

00:07:09.530 --> 00:07:13.216
We're about to enter in a time like we've never seen before.

00:07:13.216 --> 00:07:21.240
Even more with all the wars and the rumors of wars, an acceleration above everything we've ever seen before.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:28.480
And I'm telling you by the spirit of God, we're about to see signs and wonders in these last days like we've never seen before.

00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:29.480
Oh, I don't believe that.

00:07:29.480 --> 00:07:30.291
Well, that's okay.

00:07:30.291 --> 00:07:32.760
You don't have to experience it.

00:07:32.760 --> 00:07:45.280
I believe with all my heart that we're about to see God show up and show off in our lives and demonstrations and manifestations of the glory.

00:07:45.280 --> 00:07:57.070
And I have expectation for what God is about to do in the latter part of this year going into 2027.

00:07:57.080 --> 00:08:19.909
As I was looking to the east, you know, whenever you see things and he talks about martyrs and he was talking to me about martyrs in the body of Christ and he was saying that there's a lot of people he said there'll be a lot of martyrs in the days ahead.

00:08:19.919 --> 00:08:24.230
I said I don't really like that.

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:30.150
He said, Well, Brandon, there will be a lot of martyrs in the days ahead.

00:08:30.160 --> 00:08:37.070
I saw certain people that I'm familiar with on stages preaching and they just went home.

00:08:37.080 --> 00:08:42.959
I watched them as they were preaching the gospel and they were taken out by sniper.

00:08:42.959 --> 00:08:45.920
Couldn't figure out why the covering wasn't there.

00:08:45.920 --> 00:08:47.530
I was praying over these things.

00:08:47.530 --> 00:08:51.200
I said, So, are you asking me to change this?

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.800
What are you at?

00:08:52.800 --> 00:08:54.000
What is this?

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:56.120
Why are you showing me this?

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:57.920
And he said, Some people will come home.

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:05.531
He talked about sovereignty today.

00:09:05.531 --> 00:09:12.590
He talked a lot about things that are very hard for me to talk about.

00:09:12.600 --> 00:09:17.720
And he said, My sovereign hand will move the people.

00:09:17.720 --> 00:09:19.570
I saw the people moving.

00:09:19.570 --> 00:09:22.520
I saw great migration again.

00:09:22.520 --> 00:09:25.600
I saw this nation shaking.

00:09:25.600 --> 00:09:29.720
I saw things that were frightening to me a little bit in the natural.

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:34.360
And as I got fearful, he yelled three times, Fear not, Brandon.

00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:35.000
Fear not.

00:09:35.640 --> 00:09:42.590
Fear not for what you're looking at, for what's coming.

00:09:42.600 --> 00:09:44.760
Keep your eyes on me.

00:09:44.760 --> 00:09:47.760
I will hide you in the cliff of the rock.

00:09:47.760 --> 00:09:58.760
1 Corinthians 5:5 will start to come to full manifestation, a shaking and an awakening of the bride to bring her to my side.

00:09:58.760 --> 00:10:03.360
For there is a slumber upon the nations.

00:10:03.360 --> 00:10:12.080
There is, they're asleep and there will be an awakening unto God.

00:10:12.080 --> 00:10:15.680
Awakening unto God for what is about to take place.

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:20.812
And it will be around the world for the bride is asleep.

00:10:20.812 --> 00:10:22.710
A lot of them.

00:10:22.720 --> 00:10:29.760
And this is one last call, for the sun is setting on this dispensation of grace.

00:10:29.760 --> 00:10:32.040
The sun is setting.

00:10:32.040 --> 00:10:43.940
And as I saw a building exploding—it looked like some kind of device, a nuclear device or something in a building up northeast—it was a major building.

00:10:43.940 --> 00:10:48.520
And I saw it; I saw this device going off up northeast.

00:10:48.520 --> 00:10:49.832
It looked like nuclear.

00:10:49.832 --> 00:10:51.720
Something happens.

00:10:51.720 --> 00:10:54.850
I saw something very, very tragic taking place.

00:10:54.850 --> 00:11:04.270
And then I saw the headlines in the papers, and I saw, 'Terror strikes again.

00:11:04.280 --> 00:11:05.107
Terror strikes again.

00:11:05.107 --> 00:11:13.800
' And then I saw in the headlines, 'Terror in the heartland.

00:11:13.800 --> 00:11:21.169
' A nation in turmoil.

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:30.240
I saw this in the headlines in black bold letters: 'Nation in Turmoil.

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:35.830
' I wasn't going to jump right into this, but I don't want to waste your time.

00:11:35.840 --> 00:11:42.560
I have such an urgency in my heart to tell you: you must wake up.

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:44.800
