" Good job.

00:14:16.480 --> 00:14:17.320
It's coming.

00:14:19.160 --> 00:14:25.120
The Lord said it's coming and the shaking of Cuba is coming.

00:14:25.120 --> 00:14:27.680
I truly believe this with all my heart.

